@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dinkpv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.51
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos(v1))
    v2 = (v1 * (0.47 + wp.exp(tmp + 0.15)))
    v0 = ((0.96 + 0.44) * wp.abs(tmp))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.37 / v2 + 0.91)) - (v0 / (tmp + 0.91 / v1 + 0.29)))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
